
Download Android SDK / Android Studio 
(if you install Android Studio, SDK is installed automatically)
vi ~/.bash_profile
export ANDROID_HOME=/Users/rajej/Library/Android/sdk
export PATH=${PATH}:$ANDROID_HOME/tools:$ANDROID_HOME/platform-tools
Save the file
In terminal type source ~/.bash_profile
To verify the setup type echo $PATH
You should see the above android sdk path
Type the below command from any folder
adb devices 
It should show connected devices
